    <script>
        // Article data for modal content
        const serviceData = {
            1: {
                title: "Request a Quote Today",
                content: `<p class="mb-4">Ready to get started with your construction cost estimate? Our team of expert estimators is here to provide you with accurate, detailed cost estimates for your project.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">When you request a quote from Benny Estimates, you'll receive a comprehensive breakdown of all project costs including materials, labor, equipment, and contingency allowances. We analyze your project plans and specifications to ensure nothing is overlooked.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Our estimating process is thorough and efficient. We typically deliver preliminary estimates within 24-48 hours, with detailed takeoffs and cost breakdowns following shortly after.</p>
                <p>Contact us today at <a href="mailto:Ben@bennyestimates.com" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Ben@bennyestimates.com</a> or call <a href="tel:+12898017224" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">+1 (289) 801-7224</a> to get started.</p>`
            },
            2: {
                title: "Get Estimate With 30% Off",
                content: `<p class="mb-4">Take advantage of our limited-time offer: 30% off your first construction cost estimate. This special offer gives you access to our professional estimating services at a fraction of the regular cost.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Your discounted estimate includes comprehensive material takeoffs, labor cost analysis, equipment requirements, and detailed budget breakdowns. We'll help you identify potential cost savings and value engineering opportunities.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">This offer is available for new clients and applies to estimates for residential, commercial, and industrial projects of all sizes. Don't miss this opportunity to experience the Benny Estimates difference.</p>
                <p>To claim your 30% discount, simply upload your plans or contact us at <a href="mailto:Ben@bennyestimates.com" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Ben@bennyestimates.com</a> and mention this special offer.</p>`
            },
            3: {
                title: "View Our Estimate Sample",
                content: `<p class="mb-4">Curious about the quality and detail of our cost estimates? We're happy to provide samples that demonstrate the comprehensiveness and accuracy of our work.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Our sample estimates include detailed material quantity takeoffs organized by trade and phase, labor hour calculations with current wage rates, equipment cost projections, and clear contingency allowances. Each estimate provides complete transparency in how costs are calculated.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">You'll see how we break down complex projects into manageable components, making it easy to understand where every dollar is allocated. Our estimates are designed to be useful for bidding, budgeting, and project management.</p>
                <p>Contact us to request a sample estimate tailored to your project type. We'll show you why contractors trust Benny Estimates for their most important projects.</p>`
            },
            4: {
                title: "Cost Estimates Service",
                content: `<p class="mb-4">Our cost estimating service provides accurate, itemized cost breakdowns that help contractors bid confidently and win more projects. We analyze every aspect of your construction drawings to ensure comprehensive coverage.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Each estimate includes detailed material quantities with current market pricing, labor hours based on industry productivity standards, equipment requirements with rental or ownership costs, and appropriate contingency allowances for project risks.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">We tailor our estimates to your specific needs, whether you require preliminary budgets for project feasibility, detailed bids for competitive tendering, or cost models for value engineering studies.</p>
                <p>Our estimates are delivered in clear, organized formats that are easy to understand and present to clients, lenders, or project stakeholders.</p>`
            },
            5: {
                title: "Material Takeoffs Service",
                content: `<p class="mb-4">Material takeoffs are the foundation of accurate construction estimating. Our takeoff service provides detailed quantity calculations for all materials required in your project, organized by trade and phase for easy procurement.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">We quantify materials from your drawings with precision, accounting for waste factors, overlaps, and industry standards. Our takeoffs include comprehensive breakdowns of concrete, rebar, structural steel, lumber, drywall, finishes, and specialty materials.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Digital takeoffs allow us to quickly update quantities when project changes occur, ensuring your estimates always reflect current scope. We work with digital plans in PDF, CAD, or BIM formats.</p>
                <p>Accurate material takeoffs prevent costly shortages or overages, help you negotiate better supplier pricing, and provide the foundation for reliable cost estimates.</p>`
            },
            6: {
                title: "Budget Estimating Service",
                content: `<p class="mb-4">Our budget estimating service helps you develop realistic project budgets from the earliest planning stages. We provide cost models that allow you to make informed decisions about project scope, materials, and design alternatives.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Budget estimates are prepared using historical data, industry benchmarks, and current market pricing to provide reliable cost projections before detailed drawings are complete. We help you identify potential cost issues early when changes are easiest and least expensive.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">As your project develops, we refine budget estimates with increasing detail, providing cost control throughout design and construction. Our budget tracking helps you identify variances early and take corrective action.</p>
                <p>Whether you're planning a new development, renovation, or capital improvement, our budget estimating services provide the financial clarity you need for successful project delivery.</p>`
            },
            7: {
                title: "Upload Plans and Save 30%",
                content: `<p class="mb-4">Ready to get started? Upload your construction plans, blueprints, or drawings and receive a comprehensive cost estimate with 30% off your first order.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Simply upload your digital files through our secure platform. We accept PDF, CAD, and BIM formats. Once received, our estimators will review your project and provide a detailed cost breakdown within 24-48 hours.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">Your discounted estimate includes complete material takeoffs, labor cost analysis, equipment requirements, and comprehensive budget documentation. We'll also provide value engineering suggestions to help optimize your project costs.</p>
                <p>Don't wait – this limited-time offer won't last forever. Upload your plans today and discover why contractors trust Benny Estimates for their most important projects.</p>`
            },
            8: {
                title: "Contact Us Now",
                content: `<p class="mb-4">Ready to discuss your project? Our team of estimating professionals is ready to help you with any questions about our services, process, or how we can support your specific needs.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">When you contact Benny Estimates, you'll speak with experienced estimators who understand construction from the ground up. We'll discuss your project requirements, timeline, and how our services can help you achieve your goals.</p>
                <p class="mb-4">We're available to answer questions about our estimating process, provide references from satisfied clients, and discuss how we can tailor our services to your unique project requirements.</p>
                <p>Reach out today via email at <a href="mailto:Ben@bennyestimates.com" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">Ben@bennyestimates.com</a> or call us at <a href="tel:+12898017224" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400">+1 (289) 801-7224</a>. We're here to help!</p>`
            }
        };

        // Open modal function - defined globally
        window.openModal = function(serviceId) {
            console.log('Opening modal for service:', serviceId);
            const modalOverlay = document.getElementById('modalOverlay');
            const modalTitle = document.getElementById('modalTitle');
            const modalBody = document.getElementById('modalBody');
            
            const service = serviceData[serviceId];
            if (service) {
                modalTitle.textContent = service.title;
                modalBody.innerHTML = service.content;
                modalOverlay.classList.add('active');
                document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
            } else {
                console.error('Service not found:', serviceId);
            }
        }

        // Close modal function
        window.closeModal = function() {
            const modalOverlay = document.getElementById('modalOverlay');
            modalOverlay.classList.remove('active');
            document.body.style.overflow = '';
        }

        // Close modal on outside click
        window.closeModalOnOutsideClick = function(event) {
            if (event.target === document.getElementById('modalOverlay')) {
                closeModal();
            }
        }

        // Close modal with Escape key
        document.addEventListener('keydown', function(event) {
            if (event.key === 'Escape') {
                closeModal();
            }
        });

        // Theme Toggle Functionality - Fixed Version
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function() {
            const themeToggle = document.getElementById('themeToggle');
            const themeIcon = document.getElementById('themeIcon');
            const themeText = document.getElementById('themeText');
            
            // Check for saved theme preference or use default
            const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme');
            const prefersDark = window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').matches;
            const currentTheme = savedTheme || (prefersDark ? 'dark' : 'light');
            
            // Apply theme on page load
            function applyTheme(theme) {
                if (theme === 'dark') {
                    document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
                    updateThemeUI('dark', themeIcon, themeText);
                    console.log('Applied Dark Theme');
                } else {
                    document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
                    updateThemeUI('light', themeIcon, themeText);
                    console.log('Applied Light Theme');
                }
            }
            
            // Apply the theme immediately
            applyTheme(currentTheme);
            
            // Update theme UI elements
            function updateThemeUI(theme, themeIcon, themeText) {
                if (themeIcon && themeText) {
                    if (theme === 'dark') {
                        themeIcon.className = 'ri-sun-line mr-2';
                        themeText.textContent = 'Light';
                    } else {
                        themeIcon.className = 'ri-moon-line mr-2';
                        themeText.textContent = 'Dark';
                    }
                }
            }
            
            // Toggle theme function
            window.toggleTheme = function() {
                const isDark = document.documentElement.classList.contains('dark');
                
                if (isDark) {
                    // Switch to Light Mode
                    document.documentElement.classList.remove('dark');
                    localStorage.setItem('theme', 'light');
                    updateThemeUI('light', themeIcon, themeText);
                    console.log('Switched to Light Mode');
                } else {
                    // Switch to Dark Mode
                    document.documentElement.classList.add('dark');
                    localStorage.setItem('theme', 'dark');
                    updateThemeUI('dark', themeIcon, themeText);
                    console.log('Switched to Dark Mode');
                }
                
                // Force a reflow to ensure transitions work
                document.body.offsetHeight;
            }
            
            // Add event listener for theme toggle
            if (themeToggle) {
                themeToggle.addEventListener('click', toggleTheme);
            }
            
            // Listen for system theme changes
            window.matchMedia('(prefers-color-scheme: dark)').addEventListener('change', (e) => {
                if (!localStorage.getItem('theme')) {
                    const newTheme = e.matches ? 'dark' : 'light';
                    applyTheme(newTheme);
                    console.log('System theme changed to:', newTheme);
                }
            });
            
            console.log('Theme system initialized');
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>